00:04:21.545 --> 00:04:24.250
and so the density of the population

108
00:04:24.250 --> 00:04:26.456
that use cell phones is quite high

109
00:04:26.456 --> 00:04:28.128
and there's some history, there's some time

110
00:04:28.128 --> 00:04:31.158
that we can actually take a look over a period of time.

