00:04:56.038 --> 00:04:57.652
interference with sex drive.

121
00:04:57.652 --> 00:04:59.974
All these things were being reported,

122
00:04:59.974 --> 00:05:03.852
not just the most severe situations of tumor formation,

123
00:05:03.852 --> 00:05:06.661
but these other types of incidences.

124
00:05:06.661 --> 00:05:08.983
Fatigue was often reported

125
00:05:08.983 --> 00:05:12.130
associated with excessive cell phone use.

126
00:05:12.130 --> 00:05:14.533
The problem with the device,

127
00:05:14.533 --> 00:05:16.309
and you can go back to the work

128
00:05:16.309 --> 00:05:18.713
