00:05:25.748 --> 00:05:26.816
in the range of cell phones,

133
00:05:26.816 --> 00:05:28.883
precisely in the range of cell phones,

134
00:05:28.883 --> 00:05:31.217
and looking at physiological effects

135
00:05:31.217 --> 00:05:34.247
and what he found in five out of six studies

136
00:05:34.247 --> 00:05:36.964
there was actually a mutation

137
00:05:36.964 --> 00:05:39.390
in the formation of chick embryos

138
00:05:39.390 --> 00:05:41.700
because of changes to DNA structures.

139
00:05:41.700 --> 00:05:43.326
So when cell phones came out

140
00:05:43.326 --> 00:05:45.834
and Dr. Carlo's reports came out

141
00:05:45.834 --> 00:05:47.772
and then the industry said everything is safe,

142
00:05:47.772 --> 00:05:50.303
this gentleman came forward and said wait a minute,

143
00:05:50.303 --> 00:05:51.546
you know, we did these studies

144
00:05:51.546 --> 00:05:53.902
before cell phones ever existed

145
00:05:53.902 --> 00:05:55.946
and we know that energy densities

146
00:05:55.946 --> 00:05:58.012
that are equal to what cell phones produce

147
00:05:58.012 --> 00:05:59.545
in those frequency ranges

148
00:05:59.545 --> 00:06:03.887
are in fact hazardous to person's long-term health.

149
00:06:03.887 --> 00:06:06.023
And so this individual was just one.

150
00:06:06.023 --> 00:06:08.090
The other one that came forward was Ross Adey

151
00:06:08.090 --> 00:06:10.563
and Ross Adey, which is A-D-E-Y.

152
00:06:10.563 --> 00:06:11.956
If you do a search on the Internet,

153
00:06:11.956 --> 00:06:14.998
he is one of the most published scientists in the world.

