00:06:31.948 --> 00:06:35.013
would actually create a beneficial health effect,

161
00:06:35.013 --> 00:06:37.951
but the fact that it created any effect

162
00:06:37.951 --> 00:06:40.946
then moved this into the realm of the FDA.

