00:06:43.756 --> 00:06:46.798
Ross Adey also, prior to his death, came forward

165
00:06:46.798 --> 00:06:49.131
and you'll see it on the Internet with a good search.

166
00:06:49.131 --> 00:06:51.569
And he was incensed by the fact that the industry

167
00:06:51.569 --> 00:06:55.006
was dampening what the public was really entitled to know,

168
00:06:55.006 --> 00:06:57.270
that there were things that could be done.

