00:07:02.111 --> 00:07:05.478
filed by the industry to make cell phones safer.

172
00:07:05.478 --> 00:07:07.173
And we're not just talking cellular phones,

173
00:07:07.173 --> 00:07:10.888
the home portable phones actually can be potentially

174
00:07:10.888 --> 00:07:12.850
more dangerous because the energy densities

175
00:07:12.850 --> 00:07:15.196
tend to be a little more intense

176
00:07:15.196 --> 00:07:17.355
because the batteries can be recharged regularly.

177
00:07:17.355 --> 00:07:19.526
You're not worried about conserving that battery juice

178
00:07:19.526 --> 00:07:21.128
or conserving that energy.

179
00:07:21.128 --> 00:07:24.936
At the same time, the circuitry is more poorly designed

180
00:07:24.936 --> 00:07:26.605
so you have more leakage from those circuits,

