00:08:29.055 --> 00:08:30.298
so you have the wire coming in,

212
00:08:30.298 --> 00:08:32.399
you make a coil around this part,

213
00:08:32.399 --> 00:08:34.268
what happens is as the energy moves up,

214
00:08:34.268 --> 00:08:35.975
